  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 1, CHAPTER 386, LAWS OF 2025, TO RECONSTITUTE THE TAX SALES STUDY COMMITTEE; TO PROVIDE THAT APPOINTMENTS AND CERTAIN PROCEDURE EFFECTIVE BEFORE THE COMMITTEE'S DISSOLUTION SHALL BE EFFECTIVE FOR THE RECONSTITUTED COMMITTEE; TO PROVIDE A DATE ON WHICH THE STUDY COMMITTEE SHALL DISSOLVE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
